            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine sanctae et individue trinitatis. <persName ref="#people/252"
                            key="#Emperor/king">Arnolfus</persName> divina favente clementia <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">imperator</rs> augustus. Si iustis fidelium
                        petitionibus aures serenitatis nostrae dignum diiudicamus prebere, multo
                        dignius nostra auctoritate censetur, ut summi pontificis spiritalisque
                        patris nostri domni <persName ref="#people/1612" key="#Popes"
                            >Formosi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Popes">papae</rs> hortamenta toto mentis adnisu suscipere debeamus
                        et quae hortatur, intima hilaritate impendere cuicumque. Quapropter omnibus
                        fidelibus sanctae dei aecclesiae nostrisque presentibus scilicet ac futuris
                        volumus fieri notum, predictum domnum papam nostram adiisse munificentiam,
                        ut <rs key="#Monasteries"><orgName ref="#juridical_persons/53"
                                key="#Ports #Markets #Tolls #Teloneum #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium #Freeborn #Aldius #Slave"
                                >monasterium</orgName></rs> quoddam ab <persName ref="#people/55"
                            key="#Queen">Angilberga</persName>
                        <rs key="#Queen">imperatrice</rs> nepte nostra <placeName ref="#places/43"
                            >Placentie</placeName> olim constructum sub nostra <rs
                            key="#Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium">tuitione</rs> suscipientes cuncta,
                        quae inibi ab aliquibus sunt conlata, inperiali censura confirmaremus. Cuius
                        monitis libentissime obaudire conati statuimus et roborata auctoritate
                        sanccimus, ut prefatum monasterium in ipso statu persistat et ordine, quo
                        iam dicta Angilberga suo <rs key="#Testamentum">iudicatu</rs> statuit et
                        ordinavit, confirmantes omnia precessorum nostrorum <rs
                            key="#Imperial/royal_diploma">precepta</rs>, patris nostri videlicet
                            <persName ref="#people/80" key="#Emperor/king">Carlomanni</persName>,
                        qui eidem monasterio contulit <rs key="#Curtes">cortes</rs> has: <geogName
                            ref="#estates/76"
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ><placeName ref="#places/14"
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >Caput Trebium</placeName></geogName> scilicet, <geogName
                            ref="#estates/90"
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ><placeName ref="#places/612"
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >Fagetum</placeName></geogName> et <geogName ref="#estates/1504"
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ><placeName ref="#places/1920"
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >Limidi</placeName></geogName> cum omnibus apendiciis earum et quae
                        prelibata <rs key="#Queen">imperatrix</rs> adquisivit et prefato suo
                        contulit monasterio, seu ceteris omnibus, quae a quibuscumque ipsi sunt
                        tributa atque donata, ea videlicet ratione ut deinceps iam dictum coenobium
                        sub nostra imperiali tuitione ac defensione cuncta, quae ibi sunt concessa,
                        prout ipsa Angilberga voluit et iudicavit, perpetuo ac quieto iure
                        possideat, ita ut neque in mansionibus eidem pertinentibus neque in <rs
                            key="#Markets">mercato puplico</rs> neque in <rs key="#Ports">portu</rs>
                        neque in aliquo loco quilibet publice partis exactor <rs key="#Teloneum"
                            >theloneum</rs>
                        <rs key="#Tolls">ripaticum portaticum</rs> nihilque <rs
                            key="#Public_exactions">publice exactionis</rs>, quod dici aut nominari
                        potest, a rebus ipsius monasterii seu ab <rs key="#Freeborn">hominibus
                            liberis</rs> ac <rs key="#Royal_slave">servis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Aldius">aldiis ac aldianis</rs> reliquisque comendaticiis exigere
                        presumat nihilque iniuste agere in possessionibus seu hominibus ipsius
                        monasterii temerario ausu quisquam pertemptet. Contra quod si quis insurgere
                        temptaverit huiusque nostrae iussionis violator extiterit, sciat se
                        compositurum <rs key="#Penalty">viginti libras auri obrizi</rs>, medietatem
                            <rs key="#Palatium">palatio</rs> nostro et medietatem parti predicti
                        monasterii, cui fuerit inlata molestia. Quod ut verius credatur et
                        diligentius observetur, manu propria roborantes et bulla nostra subter
                        assigniri praecipientes. Signum domni Arnolfi (MF.) excellentissimi
                        imperatoris.   <persName ref="#people/1614" key="#Chancellor"
                            >Uuichingus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancillarius</rs> advicem <persName ref="#people/1613"
                            key="#Archchaplain">Teotmari</persName>
                        <rs key="#Archchaplain">archicapellani</rs> recognovi et (SR.)   Data kal.
                        mar. die anno incarnationis domini DCCCXCVI, indictione XIIII, anno imperii
                        eius primo; actum <placeName ref="#places/52">Rome</placeName>; in dei
                        nomine feliciter amen. (B.)</ab>
